'''图盖拉瀑布'''是位于南非[[德拉肯斯堡山脉|德拉肯斯堡山脉]]的一条季节性[[瀑布|瀑布]]，被认为是世界第二高的瀑布。<ref name=worldwaterfalldatabase>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/tallest-waterfalls/total-height/|title=World's tallest waterfalls by total overall height|publisher=World Waterfall Database|accessdate=20 February 2013|archive-date=2017-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429070740/http://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/tallest-waterfalls/total-height|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

瀑布共由五级组成，总落差为{{convert|948|m|abbr=on}}，最大一级的落差达411米。2016年一组来自捷克的科学考察团队测量得出983 m的落差，如果此数据得到确认，图盖拉瀑布总落差将超过当前认为世界最高的[[安赫尔瀑布|安赫尔瀑布]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.praguemonitor.com/2016/12/13/czech-surveyors-tugela-not-angel-worlds-tallest-waterfall |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-25 |archive-date=2017-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424191507/http://praguemonitor.com/2016/12/13/czech-surveyors-tugela-not-angel-worlds-tallest-waterfall |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://zpravy.aktualne.cz/domaci/k-novemu-nejvyssimu-vodopadu-na-svete-se-splha-a-brodi-atrak/r~7b14d902cc3511e6a8cb002590604f2e/?_ga=1.206758867.1583613805.1466620372 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-03-25 |archive-date=2016-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230003125/https://zpravy.aktualne.cz/domaci/k-novemu-nejvyssimu-vodopadu-na-svete-se-splha-a-brodi-atrak/r~7b14d902cc3511e6a8cb002590604f2e/?_ga=1.206758867.1583613805.1466620372 |dead-url=no }}</ref>瀑布在距[[圖蓋拉河|圖蓋拉河]]源头数公里的地方，从[[莱索托|莱索托]]和南非边境的悬崖落下。<ref name=worldwaterfalldatabase/>

